name: PS107LunchFairy
0:
”Alexa, ask Lunch Fairy what's for Lunch”
”Alexa, ask Lunch Fairy what's for Lunch tomorrow”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: lunch fairy
des: Ask the lunch fairy what's for lunch today or tomorrow and get the full menu (only works for PS 107 in Brooklyn at the moment, but may add other schools in the future). Also knows about weekends and all school holidays and will tell you there's no school for that day.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
